<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195123>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 − 17. Psathyromyia (Psathyromyia) maya Ibáñez-Bernal, May-Uc and Rebollar-Tellez sp. nov., female. 12. Head, frontal view; right antenna and left palpus removed. 13. Microphotography of cibarial armature; 14. Cibarium; 15. Antennal flagellomere 1; 16. Antennal flagellomere 2 and 3; 17. Antennal three apical flagellomeres. All measurements are expressed in millimeters, Figs. 14 and 17 at the same scale, Figs. 15 and 16 at the same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195124>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18 − 20. Psathyromyia (Psathyromyia) maya Ibáñez-Bernal, May-Uc and Rebollar-Tellez sp. nov., female. 18. Wing. 19. Abdominal sternum 2; 20. Spermathecae, spermathecal ducts and furca. All measurements are expressed in millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195124/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

